title: Ceiling, 1905–15
description: Repeating blue flower motif, foliate motif and blue flower with foliage motif all enframed by geometric shapes (resembling seven-pointed stars and stylized four-petal flowers) on a small dot background. Printed in light blues, light green, brown, tan and white liquid mica on ungrounded paper.

tombstone.epitaph:
Ceiling, 1905–15.
1905–15. Machine-printed, mica, liquid, ungrounded. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-1141.
